<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>: (و (} نَوَى الشَّيءَ <span class="c3">{يَنْوِيهِ}</span> نِيَّةً) ،<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>